'''Briletto Company''' was an arms manufacturer that developed a series of strap-on [[Laser/Legends|laser]] weapons known as [[AAP blaster box]]es, which could be affixed to [[Droid/Legends|droids]] without extensive reprogramming. The company's [[AAP-II blaster box]] was used by [[BL-series Battle Legionnaire]]s, while its [[AAP-IV blaster box]] was slated for use by [[Z-X3 experimental droid trooper]]s.<ref name="AAP blaster box" />

